high_descs: Walk to the fridge straight ahead.
Open the fridge and grab the green cup in the fridge.
Take the cup and walk to the microwave to the right.
Place the green cup next to the bowl in the microwave and heat up the green cup and remove it.
Take a step back away from the microwave.
Place the warm cup behind the roll of paper on the counter where the microwave is.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm cup on the counter where the microwave is.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the black fridge on the right.
Open the fridge, pick up the green glass from the lower left shelf and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the microwave on the counter to the left.
Put the glass inside the microwave, heat it, remove it and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the counter closest to the fridge on the right.
Put the heated glass on the left side of the counter behind the roll of paper towels.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated glass on a counter.

high_descs: Go to the fridge in front of you.
Take the green cup from inside the fridge.
Go to the counter to your right, with the microwave on it.
Put the green cup inside of the microwave, heat it up, then take it out.
Move slightly to your left, then turn to face the counter with the microwave on it.
Put the green cup on the counter, behind the paper towel roll.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm cup on the counter.
